EN: Muslims pray five times a day.

ZH: 在斋月期间，穆斯林禁食白天。
EN: During the month of Ramadan, Muslims fast during the daytime.

ZH: 穆斯林会向麦加朝圣。
EN: Muslims perform the pilgrimage to Mecca.

ZH: 穆斯林会在周五进行主日礼拜。
EN: Muslims have their main worship on Fridays.

ZH: 一些穆斯林会遵守清真食品规定。
EN: Some Muslims adhere to halal dietary laws.

ZH: 穆斯林的节日包括古尔邦节和开斋节。
EN: Muslim holidays include Eid al-Fitr and Eid al-Adha.

ZH: 在清真寺里，穆斯林会聚集祈祷。
EN: Muslims gather to pray in mosques.

